Project.Title: SWATH-MS in EF1A1- and EF1A2-deficient Schwann and MPNST cells
Project.Description: The proteins expressed in normal human Schwann and sNF96.2 MPNST cells treated with EF1A1- and EF1A2-siRNA were profiled by SWATH-MS.

Relation.Keywords: EF1A1, EF1A2, NF1,Schwann cells, MPNST, SWATH

PubMed.PubMedInfo: Kobayashi D, Tokuda T, Sato K, Okanishi H, Nagayama M, Hirayama M, Ohtsuki S, Araki N Identification of a specific translational machinery via TCTP-EF1A2 interaction regulating NF1-associated tumor growth by affinity purification and data-independent mass spectrometry acquisition (AP-DIA/SWATH). Mol Cell Proteomics. 2018 Oct 31;
